skdetail:
Flash Briefing Skill
Rated: Guidance Suggested. This skill contains: dynamic content.
des: Listen to Alexa read the latest post from the team at Austin.com, the premiere local guide to Austin, Texas! New posts are uploaded daily, from the biggest entertainment news you love to upcoming events you must not miss, and thanks to this handy Alexa skill you'll never be out of the loop again.
priv: Your requests to this skill are not shared with the skill developer.
